OL,5,CSaigon
OL,7,FThe Vietnam War is often referred to
OL,8,Fas the first "televised war". The
OL,9,Fcombination of new technologies and
OL,10,Frelatively unrestricted access to the
OL,11,Ffront lines during the 1960s and 1970s
OL,12,Fallowed journalists to bring the story
OL,13,Finto people's homes like never before.
OL,15,FFollowing the signing of the Paris
OL,16,FPeace Accords in 1973, the final
OL,17,FAmerican troops were withdrawn from
OL,18,Fcombat and financial support to South
OL,19,FVietnam was drastically cut.
