OL,7,FEmboldened, the North of the country
OL,8,Flaunched a major offensive in the
OL,9,Fspring of 1975 which would soon take
OL,10,Fthem all the way to Saigon, the former
OL,11,Fcapital of the South.
OL,13,FAt the time, ITN had two crews in
OL,14,FVietnam. Sandy Gall was teamed up with
OL,15,Fa French agency crew, whilst Michael
OL,16,FNicholson was alongside sound
OL,17,Frecordist Hugh Thomson and cameraman
OL,18,FPeter Wilkinson.
