OL,3,C'Put the camera down or we'll shoot':
OL,4,CCameraman recalls filming fall of
OL,5,CSaigon
OL,7,FAs the world remembers those images of
OL,8,Fchaos and panic 50 years on, this is
OL,9,FPeter's first-hand account of what it
OL,10,Fwas like on the other side of the
OL,11,Flens, as he captured a defining moment
OL,12,Fin history.
OL,14,FOn April 28, 1975, with the communist
OL,15,FViet Cong forces advancing towards
OL,16,FSaigon, a fierce battle broke out for
OL,17,Fcontrol of Newport Bridge on the
OL,18,Foutskirts of the city. Throughout the
OL,19,Fday, ITN's teams witnessed the intense
OL,20,Fbattle unfold up close.
