OL,3,C'Put the camera down or we'll shoot':
OL,4,CCameraman recalls filming fall of
OL,5,CSaigon
OL,7,F"You could see the Viet Cong
OL,8,Fapproaching in their APCs, and then
OL,9,Fground troops just shooting at the
OL,10,FSouth Vietnamese on the bridge. And
OL,11,Fobviously, we slowly moved backwards
OL,12,Fas they were getting closer. I think
OL,13,Fit lasted about two or three days."
OL,15,FThe situation was moving fast, and
OL,16,Fthose efforts to secure the Newport
OL,17,FBridge were ultimately in vain.
