OL,4,CCameraman recalls filming fall of
OL,5,CSaigon
OL,7,FThe next day, the Americans used the
OL,8,Fsong White Christmas to signal the
OL,9,Fstart of Operation Frequent Wind - the
OL,10,Ffinal evacuation from Saigon.
OL,12,F"Everybody wanted to get out. Leave
OL,13,FVietnam. There was lots of looting. It
OL,14,Fwas just a frightening experience,"
OL,15,FPeter recounted.
OL,17,F"We heard White Christmas about 3 am.
OL,18,FWent down to the foyer, and there were
OL,19,Fhundreds of people there queuing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
