OL,3,C'Put the camera down or we'll shoot':
OL,4,CCameraman recalls filming fall of
OL,5,CSaigon
OL,7,F"The Viet Cong warned any Americans or
OL,8,FBritish crews that were left would be
OL,9,Fshot. So, whether that was
OL,10,Fexaggerated, I don't know, but we
OL,11,Fdidn't really want to test it out"
OL,13,FPeter and his team boarded a bus
OL,14,Ftaking hopeful evacuees to the US
OL,15,Fembassy.
OL,17,F"It was horrendous. As we were driving
OL,18,Faround the streets, the bumper caught
OL,19,Fon a roll of barbed wire, which they
OL,20,Fpulled across to close the road.
