OL,3,C'Put the camera down or we'll shoot':
OL,4,CCameraman recalls filming fall of
OL,5,CSaigon
OL,7,F"We were driving down the streets with
OL,8,Fpeople attached in barbed wire.
OL,10,F"Some of them went under the bus. It
OL,11,Fwas awful. I think it lasted about
OL,12,Ffour hours."
OL,14,FPeter pulled out his camera and
OL,15,Fcaptured some of that bus ride to the
OL,16,Fembassy.
OL,18,F"The driver, who had never driven a
OL,19,Fcoach before, I was filming him from
OL,20,Fthe back.
