OL,3,C'Put the camera down or we'll shoot':
OL,4,CCameraman recalls filming fall of
OL,5,CSaigon
OL,7,F"He stopped the coach and he got out
OL,8,Fand he was shaking. And he grabbed
OL,9,Fhold of my shirt and he said, 'I'm
OL,10,Ftrying to save your life here, and
OL,11,Fthis is what you're doing to us'.
OL,13,FI said, 'No, okay, relax. You won't
OL,14,Fsee that, I promise'."
OL,16,FAfter several hours, the bus arrived
OL,17,Fat the embassy were Peter says
OL,18,Fthousands of people had been waiting
OL,19,Fthere for days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
