OL,3,C'Put the camera down or we'll shoot':
OL,4,CCameraman recalls filming fall of
OL,5,CSaigon
OL,7,F"I remember just being in that crowd
OL,8,Fand the smell and the heat of the
OL,9,Fbodies and heaving. People weren't
OL,10,Fviolent. It was quite amazing in that
OL,11,Fcrowd."
OL,13,FPeter and the team made their way to
OL,14,Fthe walls of the US embassy, waiting
OL,15,Fhours before they could scale the
OL,16,Fbuilding.
