OL,3,C'Put the camera down or we'll shoot':
OL,4,CCameraman recalls filming fall of
OL,5,CSaigon
OL,7,F"We tried to climb the wall, and our
OL,8,Ffeet were covered in excrement and
OL,9,Furine because these people had been
OL,10,Fthere for days. So, trying to climb
OL,11,Fover a wall was just so difficult.
OL,13,F"Eventually they pulled me over and I
OL,14,Fsquatted down on top of the roof of
OL,15,Fthis entrance building and started
OL,16,Ffilming.
