OL,3,C'Put the camera down or we'll shoot':
OL,4,CCameraman recalls filming fall of
OL,5,CSaigon
OL,7,F"The marines inside all had their guns
OL,8,Fpointed at me saying, 'Put that camera
OL,9,Fdown, otherwise we'll shoot you'. And
OL,10,FI actually thought, I'm not going to
OL,11,Fmake it out of this place anyway. So I
OL,12,Ffilmed it.
OL,14,F"And I carried on filming. Just filmed
OL,15,Fmy two - my soundman and Michael
OL,16,FNicholson - coming over the wall. And
OL,17,Fthat was it. I put the camera down and
OL,18,Fnot a word was said about it."
