OL,3,C'Put the camera down or we'll shoot':
OL,4,CCameraman recalls filming fall of
OL,5,CSaigon
OL,7,FThe team waited inside the compound
OL,8,Ffor hours to board one of the Chinook
OL,9,Faircrafts evacuating those lucky
OL,10,Fenough to be on the right side of the
OL,11,Fwall.
OL,13,F"It was only when we left land and
OL,14,Fwent out to the South China Sea, I
OL,15,Fsort of breathed a sigh of relief. And
OL,16,Fit (the helicopter) was absolutely
OL,17,Fpacked. There was not one inch of
OL,18,Fspace on the helicopter. So heavy. I
OL,19,Fdidn't think we were going to lift
OL,20,Feven out of the embassy."
