OL,3,C'Put the camera down or we'll shoot':
OL,4,CCameraman recalls filming fall of
OL,5,CSaigon
OL,7,FThe evacuees were taken to the USS
OL,8,FOkinawa - a US Navy ship - where they
OL,9,Fspent the evening.
OL,11,F"As evening came, lots of little boats
OL,12,Fall came out to the aircraft, hoping
OL,13,Fthat they would be saved. They were
OL,14,Fsetting fire to themselves so that
OL,15,Fthere would be a reason to be saved.
OL,16,FAnd they were all going down. It was
OL,17,Fjust horrendous, a horrendous sight."
OL,19,FFrom the USS Okinawa, Peter and his
OL,20,Fteam went to Hong Kong, before heading
OL,21,Fhome.
