OL,3,C'Put the camera down or we'll shoot':
OL,4,CCameraman recalls filming fall of
OL,5,CSaigon
OL,7,FWith the Americans gone and no
OL,8,Fresistance from the South Vietnamese,
OL,9,FSandy Gall and his crew witnessed
OL,10,Ffurther history, with the arrival of
OL,11,Fthe North Vietnamese forces into
OL,12,FSaigon on April 30, the city's fall
OL,13,Finto their hands and communist rule
OL,14,Fcomplete.
OL,16,FApril 30, 1975, marked the end of the
OL,17,FVietnam War. And it left a permanent
OL,18,Fimpression on those who covered the
OL,19,Fconflict, and whose lives were changed
OL,20,Fforever by it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
